        <p>
            <m>\textbf{Constructing angle 30째} </m>
        </p>
    
        <activity>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    <m>\textbf{ Work in pairs}</m>
                </p>
    
                <p>
                    <term>What you need: A ruler, A compass and A pencil.</term>       
                </p>

                <ol>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            Construct <m>60^\circ</m> (as shown in the above activity).
                        </p>
                            <image source="/l6.png" width="40%">
                                <shortdescription></shortdescription>
                            </image>
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        <p>
                            With <m>A</m> as center, draw an arc of radius more than half of <m>AB</m> in the interior of <m>\angle AOB</m>. With the same radius and with <m>B</m> as center draw an arc to cut the previous one at <m>C</m>.
                        </p>
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        <p>
                            Join OC. Measure <m>\angle AOC</m>.
                        </p>
                            <image source="/l7.png" width="40%">
